snippet.title: Worms Rumble Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign-up for the PC Beta starting July 15th: https://bit.ly/WormsRumbleBeta
Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/WormsRumble

Welcome to Worms Rumble, the first ever Worms game to feature real-time combat! Dive into epic 32-player Battle Royale and Deathmatch modes with full multi-platform cross-play as you fight to be the last worm standing!

Coming to PC, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 late 2020.


Official website: https://www.team17.com/games/wormsrumble/
Follow Worms on Twitter: https://twitter.com/WormsTeam17
Like Worms on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WormsTeam17/ 
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Established in 1990, Team17 is an independent developer and games label for premium games, including: the Worms, Escapists and Overcooked franchises.

We collaborate with fellow developers around the globe sharing our expertise from creation to launch across PC, console and mobile devices.

Visit https://www.team17.com for more info!
